%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22November%20was%20the%20most%20costly%20month%20of%20the%20war%20for%20Russia%20in%20terms%20of%20average%20daily%20dead%20and%20injured%3A%20UK%20intel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20in%20military%20gear%20and%20helmets%20and%20holding%20firearms%20jump%20off%20the%20top%20of%20a%20tank%20in%20a%20field%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6751829f34ef9f0108f4ce65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20servicemen%20jump%20off%20a%20T-90M%20Proryv%20tank%20during%20combat%20training%20in%20an%20undisclosed%20location%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENovember%20saw%20Russia%20hit%20a%20new%20daily%20average%20high%20for%20its%20casualties%20in%20the%20war%2C%20per%20the%20UK%20MOD.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20the%20losses%20were%20%26quot%3Blikely%20reflective%20of%20the%20higher%20tempo%20of%20Russian%20operations%26quot%3B%20against%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20was%20the%20third%20month%20in%20a%20row%20that%20Russia%20suffered%20record-breaking%20daily%20losses%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENovember%20saw%20Russia%20suffer%20a%20record%20daily%20average%20for%20the%20number%20of%20soldiers%20injured%20or%20killed%20since%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaunched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20UK%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20said%20in%20an%20intelligence%20update%20on%20Thursday%20morning%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20average%20daily%20Russian%20casualties%20(killed%20and%20wounded)%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20reached%20a%20new%20monthly%20war%20high%20during%20November%202024.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20Ukrainian%20General%20Staff%2C%20it%20said%20that%20Russia%20suffered%2045%2C680%20casualties%20in%20November%2C%20up%20from%2041%2C980%20in%20October%2C%20with%20a%20daily%20average%20of%201%2C523.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20third%20month%20in%20a%20row%20that%20Russian%20forces%20suffered%20record-breaking%20daily%20average%20losses%2C%20it%20said%2C%20and%20the%20fifth%20straight%20month%20that%20it%20had%20seen%20its%20total%20losses%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increased%20casualty%20figures%2C%20the%20UK%20MOD%20said%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Blikely%20reflective%20of%20the%20higher%20tempo%20of%20Russian%20operations%20and%20offensives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20MOD%2C%20Russia%20is%20trying%20to%20increase%20pressure%20on%20Ukraine's%20lines%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20push%20it%20back%20on%20several%20fronts%2C%20notably%20in%20Kupiansk%2C%20Toretsk%2C%20Pokrovsk%2C%20and%20Velyka%20Novosilka%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkursk-incursion-getting-tougher-losses-same-as-ukraine-front-soldiers-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Russian%20region%20of%20Kursk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20Ukraine%20partially%20occupied%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20losses%20likely%20made%20it%20the%20most%20costly%20month%20of%20the%20war%20for%20Russia%20in%20terms%20of%20personnel%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MOD%20added%20that%20Russia's%20casualties%20%26quot%3Bwill%20likely%20continue%20to%20average%20above%201%2C000%20a%20day%20in%20December%202024%20despite%20the%20onset%20of%20winter%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20continued%20attacks%20on%20multiple%20fronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20been%20relentlessly%20trying%20to%20push%20forward%20on%20multiple%20fronts%20in%20Ukraine%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20slowly%20gaining%20territory%2C%20but%20in%20a%20way%20that%20warfare%20experts%20say%20is%20