e%20are%20just%20going%20to%20push%20forward%20wave%20after%20wave%20after%20wave.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20plan%20for%20victory%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20many%20warfare%20experts%2C%20has%20been%20to%20keep%20pushing%20forward%20with%20the%20expectation%20that%20Western%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20will%20fade%20and%20that%20Ukraine's%20military%20will%20become%20increasingly%20fatigued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20scenario%20could%20result%20in%20Ukraine%20not%20having%20the%20weaponry%20it%20needs%20to%20fight%2C%20or%20for%20it%20to%20be%20pushed%20into%20a%20peace%20deal%20that%20would%20involve%20it%20giving%20territory%20and%20other%20concessions%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sets-new-average-daily-losses-record-in-ukraine-uk-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733401498000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675182d68fb3f94e507376cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sets-new-average-daily-losses-record-in-ukraine-uk-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK%20defense%20ministry%20said%20the%20average%20number%20of%20Russian%20soldiers%20killed%20or%20injured%20daily%20fighting%20Ukraine%20reached%20a%20new%20in%20November.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-sets-new-average-daily-losses-record-in-ukraine-uk-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20lauds%20Modi's%20'India%20First'%20policy%2C%20says%20Russia%20will%20'Make%20in%20India'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733401486000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fputin-lauds-