%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20having%20a%20toddler%20running%20around%2C%20but%20I%20promised%20to%20be%20more%20involved%20and%20cut%20back%20office%20hours%20if%20I%20had%20to.%20Besides%2C%20our%20daughters%20were%20older%20and%20I%20thought%20we%20would%20get%20away%20with%20a%20date%20night%20or%20two%20as%20they%20helped%20in%20watching%20their%20sibling.%20It%20all%20felt%20very%20natural%20and%20exciting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c04dfef8-b882-49e3-ab9f-5b0ab0676125%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20a%20baby%20in%20our%2040s%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20third%20pregnancy%20was%20a%20different%20experience.%20My%20wife%20had%20complications%20with%20pre-eclampsia%20and%20high%20blood%20pressure.%20She%20had%20to%20stay%20in%20bed%20for%20her%20entire%20third%20trimester%2C%20and%20I%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20task%20of%20holding%20down%20the%20fort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Sophia%20and%20Leila%20were%20older%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20keep%20them%20on%20a%20schedule.%20And%20by%20the%20time%20baby%20Mason%20made%20his%20earth%20debut%2C%20the%20family%20was%20well-structured%2C%20or%20so%20I%20thought.%20I%20was%20excited%20about%20having%20a%20son%2C%20and%20I%20kept%20the%20promise%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20time%20at%20work%20and%20be%20more%20present%20with%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20time%20for%20my%20wife%20to%20recover%20after%20having%20our%20son.%20Her%20progress%20wasn't%20as%20swift%20as%20it%20was%20when%20she%20had%20our%20daughters%20in%20her%20early%2030s.%20That%20in%20itself%20presented%20a%20challenge%20as%20I%20continuously%20worried%20about%20her%20overall%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228036b29b-21c4-4288-a3c1-0bb8499b4859%5C%22%3ESleep%20deprivation%20is%20harder%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20most%20babies%2C%20our%20son%20constantly%20keeps%20us%20up%20at%20night.%20He%20isn't%20a%20good%20sleeper.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESleep%20deprivation%20has%20become%20a%20constant%20enemy%2C%20and%20waking%20up%20tired%20is%20the%20norm.%20In%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%2C%20it's%20all%20worth%20it%2C%20but%20when%20you%20have%20to%20report%20early%20to%20work%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20it's%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMason%20is%202.5%20years%20old%20now%2C%20and%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20have%20had%20to%20give%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20quality%20time.%20The%20last%20time%20we%20went%20out%20on%20a%20date%20night%20was%20a%20year%20ago.%20Our%20daughters%20are%20not%20exactly%20keen%20on%20babysitting.%20They%20are%20out%20with%20their%20friends%20and%20living%20their%20lives%20most%20days%20(and%20nights)%2C%20and%20we%20encourage%20them%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20was%20doing%20the%20same%20in%20my%20teenage%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20are%20older%2C%20wiser%2C%20and%20more%20financially%20secure%2C%20we%20are%20still%20struggling%20with%20the%20common%20elements%20of%20parenting%20in%20our%2040s.%20We've%20had%20to%20re-learn%20things%20like%20carrying%20our%20son%20around%20during%20errands%2C%20learning%20how%20to%20make%20baby%20food%20again%2C%20keeping%20late%20nights%2C%20and%20singing%20lullabies%2C%20but%20we%20are%20getting%20better%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20content%20with%20how%20we%20raised%20our%20first%20two%20kids%20and%20I%20don't%20intend%20to%20drop%20the%20ball%20with%20this%20one.%20We%20still%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20learning%2C%20re-learning%20and%20unlearning%20to%20do%2C%20but%20we%20are%20getting%20there%2C%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvinced-wife-have-another-baby-in-40s-its-not-easy-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733396941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673f3f6cfa0140cdd564a2d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvinced-wife-have-another-baby-in-40s-its-not-easy-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20both%20always%20wanted%20to%20have%20three%20kids.%20When%20our%20daughters%20were%20teens%2C%20I%20convinced%20my%20wife%20to%20have%20one%20more%20baby.%20Sleep%20deprivation%20has%20been%20hard.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nate%20Giovanni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvinced-wife-have-another-baby-in-40s-its-not-easy-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Targets%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20Alleging%20George%20Soros%20Link%2C%20Congress%20Cries%20Foul%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20went%20to%20the%20mattresses%20in%20Parliament%20Thursday%20after%20the%20former%20accused%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20of%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Btraitor%20of%20the%20highest%20order%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20attack%20naming%20him%2C%20%26quot%3Bsome%20agencies%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20and%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20triangle%20trying%20to%20destabilise%20India%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20responded%20swiftly%20and%20strongly%2C%20condemning%20the%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20also%20calling%20out%20another%20BJP%20MP%2C%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20for%20%26quot%3Bmost%20derogatory%20words%26quot%3B%20targeting%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20the%20newly%20elected%20Wayanad%20MP%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20opposition%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20that%20followed%20Mr%20Dubey's%20furious%20attack%20prompted%20chaos%20in%2C%20and%20a%20temporary%20adjournment%20of%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20A%20similar%20ruckus%20consumed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20after%20the%20BJP's%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20alleged%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%20and%20conspicuous%20attacks%20on%20national%20interest%20from%20abroad%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concerted%20attack%20followed%20a%20news%20report%20by%20French%20publication%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediapart.fr%2Fen%2Fjournal%2Finternational%2F021224%2Fhidden-links-between-giant-investigative-journalism-and-us-government%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediapart%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20claims%20%26quot%3Bhidden%20links%20between%20a%20giant%20of%20investigative%20journalism%20(referring%20to%20the%20OCCRP%2C%20the%20Organized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20an%20Amsterdam-based%20news%20network)%20and%20the%20US%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMediapart%20said%20the%20OCCRP%2C%20which%20calls%20itself%20%26quot%3Bthe%20largest%20investigative%20reporting%20organization%20on%20Earth%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20financially%20and%20structurally%20dependent%20on%20the%20United%20States.%20According%20to%20Mediapart%20the%20OCCRP%20also%20receives%20millions%20in%20funding%20from%20European%20countries%20like%20France%20and%20Sweden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MP%20Sambit%20Patra%20set%20the%20ball%20rolling%20this%20morning%20with%20a%20heated%20press%20conference%20in%20which%20he%20declared%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20this%20triangle...%20on%20one%20side%20George%20Soros%20from%20America%20(and)%20some%20agencies%20of%20America%20and%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20is%20a%20big%20news%20portal%20named%20OCCRP%20...%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Patra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Soros%20is%20a%20controversial%20figure%20in%20India%2C%20with%20the%20right%20wing%20accusing%20him%20of%20funding%20anti-India%20elements%20and%20supporting%20regime%20change%20across%20the%20world%20to%20push%20the%20West's%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20over%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20frequently%20linked%20the%20Congress%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20to%20Mr%20Soros%2C%20and%20to%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20-%20on%20issues%20like%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware%20scandal%20and%20the%20Covaxin%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20-%20based%20on%20reports%20by%20the%20OCCRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%2C%20and%20most%20important%20side%2C%20is%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20-%20a%20traitor%20of%20the%20highest%20order.%20I%20am%20not%20scared%20to%20say%20this%20word...%20I%20don't%20have%20any%20hesitation%20in%20calling%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20a%20traitor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patra%20accused%20Mr%20Gandhi%20of%20betraying%20India%20and%20claimed%20he%20follows%20OCCRP%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOCCRP%20is%20a%20global%20media%20agency%20and%20crores%20of%20people%20read%20what%20they%20publish.%20Open%20Society%20Foundation%20is%20a%20big%20funder...%20it%20is%20George%20Soros's%20foundation.%20Such%20agencies%20work%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20people%20who%20fund%20them%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20betraying%20the%20whole%20country...%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20charge%20was%20picked%20up%20and%20repeated%20by%20the%20BJP's%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20triggering%20vociferous%20protests%20from%20the%20Congress.%20Mr%20Dubey%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20%26quot%3Bconspiring%20with%20foreign%20forces%26quot%3B%20to%20derail%20the%20government%20because%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Bhatred%26quot%3B%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Delhi%20%7C%20On%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWas%20Salil%20Shetty%20not%20in%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3F%20Is%20he%20not%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Soros%20Foundation%3F%20Did%20they%20not%20meet%20Ilhan%20Omar%2C%20Barbara%20Lee%2C%20or%20Ro%20Khanna%2C%20who%20wrote%20a%20letter%20in%20America%20asking%20to%20boycott%20the%20PM%20and%20not%20address%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFm7Y40pUpH%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFm7Y40pUpH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1864607180131062069%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGeorge%20Soros%20routinely%20conspires%20to%20derail%20economies%20of%20other%20countries.%20He%20was%20the%20force%20behind%20the%20closure%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%20in%201991.%20He%20accrued%20benefits%20of%20over%20Rs%206%20billion%20from%20this.%20Today%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20derail%20the%20Indian%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%2C%20nearly%20drowned%20out%20by%20shouting%20Congress%20MPs%20and%20his%20BJP%20colleagues%20thumping%20their%20desks%20in%20approval%2C%20also%20demanded%20Mr%20Gandhi%20be%20investigated%20for%20meeting%20with%20American%20lawmakers%20like%20Ilhan%20Omar%2C%20who%20are%20vocal%20critics%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20his%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20must%20answer...%20what%20transpired%20in%20meetings%20with%20those%20who%20have%20a%20history%20of%20peddling%20anti-India%20agenda%20on%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20foreign%20tours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Hits%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20bemoaned%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20unfortunate%20incident%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Honourable%20Speaker%20allowed%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20to%20speak%20during%20Zero%20Hour.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20the%20most%20derogatory%20words%20were%20used%20against%20the%20LoP%20and%20the%20Wayanad%20MP%20(Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra)%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20entire%20Congress%20party%2C%20which%20is%20unacceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20leader%20KC%20Venugopal%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%2