%2FdBxcL%2F2%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Weekly%20mortgage%20rates%20over%20the%20last%205%20years%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22503%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20Factors%20Influence%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20Factors%20Influence%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhow-are-mortgage-rates-determined%5C%22%3EMortgage%20rates%20are%20determined%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20different%20factors%2C%20including%20larger%20economic%20trends%2C%20Federal%20Reserve%20policy%2C%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fstate-mortgage-rates%5C%22%3Estate's%20current%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20type%20of%20loan%20you're%20getting%2C%20and%20your%20personal%20financial%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20of%20these%20factors%20are%20out%20of%20your%20control%2C%20you%20can%20work%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fhow-to-improve-credit-score%5C%22%3Eimproving%20your%20credit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20paying%20off%20debt%2C%20and%20saving%20for%20a%20larger%20down%20payment%20to%20ensure%20you%20get%20the%20best%20rate%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20Does%20the%20Fed%20Rate%20Affect%20Mortgage%20Rates%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed%20increased%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-the-federal-funds-rate%5C%22%3Efederal%20funds%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20dramatically%20in%202022%20and%202023%20to%20try%20to%20slow%20economic%20growth%20and%20get%20inflation%20under%20control.%20Inflation%20has%20since%20slowed%20significantly%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20bit%20above%20the%20Fed's%202%25%20target%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20aren't%20directly%20impacted%20by%20changes%20to%20the%20federal%20funds%20rate%2C%20but%20they%20often%20trend%20up%20or%20down%20ahead%20of%20Fed%20policy%20moves.%20This%20is%20because%20mortgage%20rates%20change%20based%20on%20investor%20demand%20for%20mortgage-backed%20securities%2C%20and%20this%20demand%20is%20often%20impacted%20by%20how%20investors%20expect%20Fed%20policy%20to%20affect%20the%20broader%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFed%20officials%20lowered%20rates%20at%20their%20meetings%20in%20September%20and%20November%2C%20and%20they're%20expected%20to%20continue%20cutting%20rates%20at%20future%20meetings.%20This%20should%20help%20mortgage%20rates%20trend%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Will%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Drop%20in%20November%3F%5C%22%3EWill%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Drop%20in%20December%202024%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20increased%20in%20November%2C%20but%20they've%20been%20slightly%20lower%20so%20far%20this%20month.%20Where%20they%20go%20next%20depends%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20unknowns%2C%20so%20we'll%20need%20more%20data%20to%20see%20how%20inflation%20and%20the%20labor%20market%20are%20trending.%20In%20general%2C%20rates%20aren't%20expected%20to%20drop%20again%20until%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20Low%20Will%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Go%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20are%20unlikely%20to%20drop%20back%20down%20to%20the%20historic%20lows%20of%202020%20and%202021%2C%20when%2030-year%20fixed%20rates%20fell%20below%203%25.%20But%20rates%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20to%20ease%20throughout%20the%20next%20year%20or%20two%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20rates%20could%20ultimately%20settle%20in%20closer%20to%206%25%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWill%20Mortgage%20Rates%20Go%20Down%20in%202025%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20major%20forecasts%20expect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fwill-mortgage-rates-go-down-this-year%5C%22%3Emortgage%20rates%20to%20go%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20throughout%202025%20as%20the%20Fed%20continues%20to%2