3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Mission%20A%20Success%2C%20Places%20European%20Sun-Observation%20Satellites%20In%20Orbit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation's%20(ISRO)%20workhorse%20rocket%20PSLV%20today%20successfully%20achieved%20its%20launch%20objectives%2C%20deploying%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%20Proba-3%20satellite%20into%20its%20%26quot%3Bdesignated%20orbit%20with%20precision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PSLV%20rocket%20lifted%20off%20today%20at%204%3A04%20pm%20from%20the%20Sriharikota%20launch%20station%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20carrying%20the%20Proba-3%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%9C%85%20Mission%20Success!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20PSLV-C59%2FPROBA-3%20Mission%20has%20successfully%20achieved%20its%20launch%20objectives%2C%20deploying%20ESA's%20satellites%20into%20their%20designated%20orbit%20with%20precision.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%F0%9F%8C%8C%20A%20testament%20to%20the%20trusted%20performance%20of%20PSLV%2C%20the%20collaboration%20of%20NSIL%20and%20ISRO%2C%20and%20ESA's%20innovative%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1864624104294248477%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%205%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20launch%20was%20postponed%20yesterday%20after%20an%20'anomaly'%20was%20detected%20in%20the%20satellites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%2061st%20flight%2C%20India's%20workhorse%20rocket%2C%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%2C%20has%20been%20tasked%20by%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%20to%20launch%20a%20unique%20pair%20of%20satellites%20designed%20to%20simulate%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20through%20precision%20formation%20flying%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20stated%20that%20the%20vehicle%20will%20place%20the%20Proba-3%20spacecraft%20into%20a%20highly%20elliptical%20orbit%20as%20part%20of%20a%20dedicated%20commercial%20mission%20under%20New%20Space%20India%20Limited%20(NSIL)%2C%20ISRO's%20commercial%20arm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProba-3%20is%20an%20in-orbit%20demonstration%20(IOD)%20mission%20by%20the%20ESA%2C%20aiming%20to%20showcase%20advanced%20formation-flying%20technologies.%20It%20consists%20of%20two%20spacecraft%3A%20the%20Coronagraph%20Spacecraft%20(CSC)%20and%20the%20Occulter%20Spacecraft%20(OSC).%20These%20will%20be%20launched%20together%20in%20a%20stacked%20configuration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeighing%20a%20combined%20545%20kg%2C%20the%20two%20satellites%20will%20be%20carried%20into%20space%20by%20the%2044.5-meter-tall%20PSLV%20rocket%2C%20which%20weighs%20320%20tonnes%20at%20lift-off.%20Approximately%2018%20minutes%20after%20launch%2C%20the%20satellites%20will%20be%20deployed%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%20600%20km%20above%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Proba-3%20mission%20involves%20two%20mini-satellites%20flying%20in%20close%20formation%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20precisely%20control%20their%20attitude%20and%20separation.%20This%20innovative%20configuration%20simulates%20a%20total%20solar%20eclipse%20and%20demonstrates%20cutting-edge%20formation-flying%20and%20rendezvous%20technologies.%20According%20to%20ISRO%2C%20Proba-3%20is%20ESA's-and%20the%20world's-first%20precision%20formation-flying%20mission.%20The%20satellites%20will%20maintain%20a%20fixed%20configuration%20as%20if%20they%20were%20a%20single%20rigid%20structure%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%20second%20ESA%20satellite%20launch%20aboard%20an%20Indian%20rocket.%20The%20first%2C%20the%20Proba-1%20mission%2C%20was%20launched%20in%202001%20using%20the%20PSLV.%20Originally%20planned%20as%20a%20one-year%20mission%2C%20Proba-1%20has%20exceeded%20expectations%2C%20remaining%20operational%20for%20over%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733396280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fjdtt1bcg_isro-proba-3_625x300_05_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-rocket-carrying-european-sun-observation-satellite-proba-3-lifts-off-from-sriharikota-7178407%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation's%20(ISRO)%20workhorse%20rocket%20PSLV%20successfully%20achieved%20its%20launch%20objectives%2C%20deploying%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20(ESA)%20Proba-3%20satellites.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fisro-rocket-carrying-european-sun-observation-satellite-proba-3-lifts-off-from-sriharikota-7178407%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bitcoin%20crosses%20%24100%2C000%20milestone%3A%20Should%20Indians%20invest%20in%20crypto%20now%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733396237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ffinance%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbitcoin-crosses-100-000-milestone-should-indians-invest-in-crypto-now-124120500749_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20investors%20are%20now%20viewing%20Bitcoin%20as%20a%20viable%20option%20for%20wealth%20creation%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BharatPe%20launches%20offering%20to%20protect%20users%20from%20digital%20transaction%20frauds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733396147000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbharatpe-launches-offering-to-protect-users-from-digital-transaction-frauds-124120500748_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BharatPe%20Shield%20covers%20risks%20such%20as%20computer%20fraud%2C%20phishg%20attacks%2C%20and%20unauthorised%20transactions%