ther.%20The%20complainant%2C%20Arjun%2C%20told%20them%20no%20household%20items%20were%20missing.%20Therefore%2C%20robbery%20was%20ruled%20out.%20The%20police's%20investigation%20did%20not%20point%20to%20any%20dispute%20between%20the%20family%20and%20their%20neighbours.%20No%20angle%20of%20personal%20animosity%20was%20found%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20then%20turned%20to%20the%20son.%20%26quot%3BThe%20version%20of%20son%20of%20the%20deceased%20was%20found%20suspicious%20as%20there%20were%20lots%20of%20contradictions%20in%20his%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20statement%20said.%20Initially%2C%20Arjun%20tried%20to%20mislead%20the%20investigation.%20But%20he%20broke%20down%20during%20the%20interrogation%20and%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020-year-old%20second-year%20student%20of%20Delhi%20University%20then%20shared%20numbing%20details%20of%20how%20he%20planned%20to%20murder%20his%20parents%20and%20his%20sister%20and%20why%20he%20did%20it.%20A%20trained%20state-level%20boxer%2C%20Arjun%20told%20police%20that%20he%20had%20chosen%20the%20day%20of%20the%20crime%20carefully%20--%20it%20was%20his%20parents'%20marriage%20anniversary.%20This%20pointed%20to%20the%20hate%20the%20young%20man%20had%20nursed%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20police%20that%20his%20father%20was%20an%20Army%20veteran%20and%20scolded%20him%20for%20not%20studying%20hard.%20A%20recent%20incident%20during%20which%20his%20father%20scolded%20and%20thrashed%20him%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20tipping%20point.%20%26quot%3BDue%20to%20this%20insult%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20he%20felt%20deeply%20humiliated.%20He%20had%20(a)%20deep%20grudge%20against%20his%20father%20and%20family%20members%20as%20no%20one%20(would)%20support%20him.%20He%20used%20to%20feel%20neglected%20and%20isolated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20recently%20came%20to%20know%20that%20his%20father%20had%20decided%20to%20give%20away%20property%20to%20his%20sister%20Kavita.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20his%20parents'%20death%20anniversary%2C%20he%20stabbed%20them%20and%20his%20sister%20to%20death%20with%20a%20knife%20in%20their%20sleep.%20Some%20reports%20say%20it%20was%20an%20Army%20knife%20that%20belonged%20to%20his%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20create%20a%20web%20of%20deception%2C%20he%20went%20out%20at%205.30%20am%20to%20have%20(an)%20alibi%20so%20that%20nobody%20could%20have%20suspicion%20on%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20neighbour%2C%20Arjun%20told%20them%20that%20he%20had%20wished%20his%20parents%20a%20happy%20wedding%20anniversary%20before%20going%20for%20a%20walk%20and%20returned%20to%20find%20them%20dead.%20%26quot%3BThe%20son%20told%20us%20that%20he%20went%20out%20for%20a%20morning%20walk%20and%20when%20he%20returned%20he%20saw%2C%20his%20parents%20and%20sister%20had%20been%20stabbed%20to%20death%20and%20there%20was%20blood%20all%20around.%20He%20told%20us%20it%20was%20their%20marriage%20anniversary%20and%20went%20out%20after%20wishing%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20neighbour%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoint%20Police%20Commissioner%2C%20Southern%20Range%2C%20SK%20Jain%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20questioning%2C%20we%20found%20contradictions%20in%20Arjun's%20statements.%20Eventually%2C%20he%20confessed%20that%20he%20killed%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733395320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Ftdr6285_delhi-triple-murder_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneb-sarai-delhi-triple-murder-bruised-ego-sibling-rivalry-behind-young-boxer-murdering-parents-sister-7178463%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajesh%20Kumar%20(51)%2C%20his%20wife%20Komal%20(46)%20and%20their%20daughter%20Kavita%20(23)%20were%20found%20dead%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Delhi's%20Neb%