e.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20note%2C%20if%20India%20decides%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20the%20ICC%20members%20will%20have%20to%20forego%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20%24750%20million%20(total%20value%20of%20the%20media%20rights).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20Pakistan%20decides%20to%20opt%20out%2C%20the%20ICC%20members%20will%20have%20to%20forego%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20report%2C%20industry%20sources%20said%20-%20%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20is%20well%20within%20its%20rights%20to%20shift%20the%20tournament%20to%20any%20country%20as%20long%20as%20it%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20the%20property%20(read%3A%20Champions%20Trophy).%20The%20decision%20is%20not%20so%20complicated%20as%20it%20is%20being%20made%20to%20look%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20question%20of%20the%20tournament%20getting%20cancelled.%20As%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20saying%20they%20will%20do%20a%20quid-pro%20with%20India%20when%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20arrives%2C%20let's%20be%20clear%20that%20the%20current%20topic%20is%20an%20ICC%20matter.%20The%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20for%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20to%20decide.%20Neither%20is%20the%20federation%20the%20same%2C%20nor%20the%20broadcaster%20and%20it's%20a%20completely%20separate%20issue%20for%20PCB%20to%20think%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733395020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fh11amgco_india-pakistan-afp_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshould-india-pull-out-broadcaster-note-makes-startling-champions-trophy-revelation-7176756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20wait%20continues%20for%20any%20decision%20regarding%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20following%20India's%20refusal%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20due%20to%20security%20reasons.%22%2C%22