re%20ways%20to%20cheat%20or%20be%20deceptive%20or%20be%20disloyal%20in%20a%20relationship%20than%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Landis%20Bejar%2C%20a%20wedding%20therapist%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aisle-talk.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAisleTalk%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20lovers%20have%20turned%20to%20%26quot%3Bloyalty%20tests%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20if%20their%20partners%20are%20faithful%2C%20tapping%20strangers%20to%20catch%20their%20significant%20others%20being%20disloyal%20by%20sending%20incriminating%20direct%20messages%2C%20hoping%20for%20an%20untoward%20reply.%20Now%2C%20companies%20like%20Lazo%20and%20Loyalty-Test%20are%20cashing%20in%20on%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20who%20paid%20to%20test%20her%20partner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20wished%20she%20had%20used%20the%20service%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224a61089-7e0b-44f4-84e0-6e4930c18f72%5C%22%3EHelping%20others%20who%20get%20cheated%20on%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tester%20who%20goes%20by%20Ari%20on%20Loyalty-Test%20for%20privacy%20reasons%20but%20whose%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20BI%20said%20she%20first%20became%20familiar%20with%20the%20app%20as%20a%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20the%20one%20that%20wanted%20to%20test%20my%20partner%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20ended%20up%20passing%20by%20default.%20He%20didn't%20respond.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAri%20said%20she%20appreciated%20the%20process%20and%20became%20interested%20in%20being%20a%20tester.%20So%2C%20she%20signed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20with%20relationships%2C%20I%20would%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdated-woman-engaged-to-someone-else-cheating-lover-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunfaithful%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20I%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20have%20this%20sooner%2C%26quot%3B%20Ari%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20one%20to%20help%20people%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ari%20works%20as%20a%20hairstylist%20by%20day%20and%20performs%20between%20five%20and%20eight%20loyalty%20tests%20weekly.%20She%20sticks%20to%20digital%20tests%20and%20charges%20%2455%20for%20a%20day%20of%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20noticed%20people%20do%20fold%20very%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20usually%20happens%20within%20the%20first%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20conversation%20on%20Loyalty-Tests.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67338b26192f52589857e516%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20testers%20send%20screenshots%20of%20their%20progress.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Loyalty-Tests%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAri%20said%20she%20starts%20her%20work%20with%20clients%20by%20asking%20what%20they%20think%20of%20as%20a%20pass%20or%20fail%20to%20ensure%20they%20agree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUsually%2C%20I'll%20explain%20the%20process%20that%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%2C%20and%20if%20they%20have%20specific%20things%20they%20want%20me%20to%20say%2C%20then%20I%20go%20by%20what%20they%20want%20me%20to%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20her%20clients%20are%20in%20committed%20relationships%20and%20suspect%20cheating%20when%20they%20hire%20her.%20Others%20are%20about%20to%20take%20a%20step%20with%20someone%2C%20like%20becoming%20exclusive%20or%20moving%20in%20together%2C%20and%20want%20to%20use%20a%20loyalty%20test%20to%20confirm%20they're%20making%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAri%20said%20it%20can%20be%20difficult%20when%20she%20has%20to%20tell%20clients%20their%20partners%20are%20failing%20a%20test%2C%20both%20because%20she%20feels%20empathy%20toward%20them%20and%20because%20she%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-cheat-scandals-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeated%3C%2Fa%3E%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20length%20that%20they%20would%20go%20to%20be%20sneaky%2C%20you%20know%2C%20it's%20a%20little%20triggering%20sometimes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e80c5e03-29d5-4612-a520-6bac6e618045%5C%22%3E'Loyalty%20tests'%20are%20on%20the%20rise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20about%20loyalty%20tests%20started%20going%20viral%20online%20around%202021%2C%20and%20they%20all%20followed%20a%20similar%20blueprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Btester%26quot%3B%20messages%20someone's%20partner%20on%20social%20media%20at%20their%20request%20and%20pretends%20to%20want%20to%20date%20them.%20If%20the%20person%20shows%20interest%20in%20the%20fake%20suitor%2C%20they%20fail%20the%20test.%20If%20they%20don't%2C%20they%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20trend%20became%20more%20popular%2C%20companies%20started%20offering%20anonymous%20tests%20for%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELazo%20began%20testing%20potential%20cheaters%20in%20January%2C%20Ashlyn%20Nakasu%2C%20the%20company's%20community%20manager%2C%20told%20BI.%20Lazo's%20team%20aims%20for%20the%20app%20to%20provide%20people%20unfettered%20access%20to%20the%20truth%20in%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELazo%20has%20about%20400%20checkers%20that%20charge%20a%20range%20of%20fees%2C%20though%20they%20typically%20start%20at%20%2440.%20For%20that%20fee%2C%20a%20tester%20will%20message%20your%20partner%2C%20pretending%20to%20be%20interested%20in%20them%20to%20see%20if%20they%20cross%20a%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20never%20know%20if%20you're%20actually%20going%20to%20get%20the%20whole%20truth%20out%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakasu%20told%20BI%2C%20as%20many%20people%20don't%20immediately%20confess%20if%20their%20partner%20accuses%20them%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforgiving-partner-who-cheated-actually-meant-forgiving-myself-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echeating%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screenshot%20of%20a%20conversation%20on%20Loyalty%20Tests.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673389d05ec9bfa3d63d8b02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221569%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20conversation%20between%20a%20tester%20and%20a%20client%20on%20Loyalty-Tests.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Loyalty-Tests%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wanted%20to%20offer%20a%20solution%20that%20was%20more%20affordable%20and%20less%20time-consuming%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakasu%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20hiring%20a%20private%20investigator.%20According%20to%20the%20job%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bark.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fprivate-investigators%2Fnew-york%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBark%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20private%20investigator%20in%20the%20US%20is%20%2485%20per%20hour%2C%20and%20their%20services%20can%20range%20from%20digital%20investigation%20to%20trailing%20your%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELoyalty-Tests%2C%20launched%20in%20January%202023%2C%20offers%20digital%20and%20in-person%20tests%20for%20a%20fee%20set%20by%20the%20testers.%20As%20founder%20and%20CEO%20Brandan%20Balasingham%20told%20BI%2C%20testers%20sign%20up%20to%20work%20for%20the%20company%20on%20the%20app%20like%20Uber%20drivers.%20The%20company%20then%20sifts%20through%20applicants%20to%20see%20who%20would%20be%20a%20good%20tester%20before%20they%20get%20approved%20to%20take%20on%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20testers%20charge%20as%20little%20as%20%2410%20for%20a%20digital%20test%2C%20but%20the%20in-person%20tests%2C%20in%20which%20a%20tester%20meets%20up%20with%20a%20potential%20cheater%20at%20a%20client's%20direction%2C%20can%20cost%20upward%20of%20%24500