ss%20the%20loyalty%20tests.%20Balasingham%20said%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20Loyalty-Tests%20shows%20a%20discrepancy%20between%20the%20results%20of%20men%20and%20women%20being%20tested.%20About%2060%25%20of%20men%20fail%2C%20while%20around%2030%25%20of%20women%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226a66af7b-1537-4234-82d4-2d27f1225ee6%5C%22%3EEstablish%20trust%20early%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20loyalty%20tests%20have%20become%20popular%2C%20Bejar%20said%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20norm%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-healthy-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20relationship%20without%20trust%2C%26quot%3B%20Bejar%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20have%20trust%2C%20we%20have%20to%20completely%20manage%20another%20person%20and%20oversee%20another%20person%20to%20ensure%20they're%20going%20to%20do%20what%20they%20say%20they%20are.%20And%20that%20can't%20work%20in%20a%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDramatic%20acts%20like%20cheating%20can%20erode%20trust%2C%20but%20smaller%20%26quot%3Bruptures%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Bejar%20calls%20them%2C%20like%20not%20doing%20something%20you%20said%20you%20would%20or%20telling%20white%20lies%2C%20can%20damage%20the%20bond%20between%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20just%20as%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20sense%2C%20conducting%20a%20loyalty%20test%20against%20your%20partner%20can%20be%20a%20betrayal%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20cheating%20is.%20Whether%20someone%20passes%20a%20loyalty%20test%20or%20not%2C%20the%20relationship%20is%20likely%20in%20trouble%20if%20someone%20feels%20the%20need%20to%20conduct%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBejar%20does%20think%20there%20are%20some%20situations%20where%20a%20loyalty%20test%20could%20be%20helpful%2C%20though%2C%20particularly%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdark-psychology-tricks-love-bombing-gaslighting-dating-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabusive%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20loyalty%20test%20can%20break%20someone%20out%20of%20that%20kind%20of%20contrived%20reality%20that%20an%20abusive%20person%20has%20created%20for%20them%2C%20that%20by%20definition%20is%20really%20hard%20to%20get%20out%20of%2C%20then%20I%20think%20there's%20a%20place%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bejar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20use%20a%20loyalty%20test%20instead%20of%20organically%20building%20trust%20with%20your%20partner%20over%20time%2C%20Bejar%20said%20that's%20likely%20a%20sign%20you%20need%20to%20reflect%20on%20why%20building%20trust%20seems%20hard.%20She%20added%20that%20you%20should%20set%20boundaries%20with%20your%20partner%20to%20ensure%20you%20agree%20on%20the%20definition%20of%20betrayal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLove%20can%20be%20blinding%2C%20and%20we%20can%20overlook%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20know%20what%20a%20dealbreaker%20is%20to%20you%20so%20that%20if%20you%20are%20in%20love%20with%20somebody%20and%20they%20cross%20one%20of%20your%20boundaries%2C%20you%20can%20walk%20away%20even%20though%20it's%20hard%20and%20sad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floyalty-test-cheating-partner-relationship-advice-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733394721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67339e145ec9bfa3d63d93b8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floyalty-test-cheating-partner-relationship-advice-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Loyalty%20tests%20have%20become%20a%20popular%20way%20to%20see%20if%20a%20partner%20is%20cheating%2C%20and%20companies%20are%20cashing%20in.%20A%20therapist%20says%20they%20are%20rarely%20a%20good%20thing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22