20no%20longer%20suffering%20as%20fears%20had%20eased%20about%20them%20being%20invaded%20by%20Russia%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbaltic-named-the-most-punctual-airline-in-the-world-by-oag-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirBaltic%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20still%20been%20hampered%20by%20airspace%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overflying%20restrictions%20are%20still%20there%20and%20everything%20which%20goes%20southeast%20is%2C%20for%20us%2C%20a%20detour%20%E2%80%94%20circumnavigating%20the%20airspace%2C%26quot%3B%20Gauss%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20has%20more%20than%2070%20destinations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Cyprus%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Dubai%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20fastest%20route%20from%20Latvia%20would%20involve%20flying%20over%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20alternative%20routes%20isn't%20simple.%20Gauss%20explained%20how%20flying%20south%20from%20the%20Baltics%2C%20there's%20only%20a%20%26quot%3Bsmall%20corridor%26quot%3B%20between%20Belarus%20and%20the%20Russian%20exclave%20of%20Kaliningrad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20that%20is%20too%20busy%2C%20we%20need%20to%20fly%20over%20Sweden%20into%20the%20south%2C%26quot%3B%20Gauss%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20there's%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20cost%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a07e1995-7ab6-4ea9-9f47-7d9e197fbaa2%5C%22%3EAirBaltic's%20turnaround%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGauss%20started%20his%20career%20as%20a%20pilot%20in%201992%20with%20Deutsche%20BA%2C%20then%20a%20low-cost%20subsidiary%20of%20British%20Airways.%20He%20then%20entered%20management%20training%20with%20the%20airline%20and%20worked%20his%20way%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20developing%20a%20reputation%20for%20turning%20around%20airlines%2C%20he%20was%20headhunted%20for%20airBaltic%20in%202011.%20The%20airline%20had%20gone%20bankrupt%2C%20but%20the%20Latvian%20government%20agreed%20to%20invest%20more%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26q