%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVoted%20In%20Favour%20Of%2010%2C%20Abstained%20From%203%20Gaza%20Resolutions%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20speaking%20in%20Parliament%20today%2C%20reaffirmed%20India's%20long-standing%20support%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20conflict%20by%20calling%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bsovereign%2C%20independent%2C%20and%20viable%20Palestinian%20state%26quot%3B%20alongside%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20claim%20during%20Question%20Hour%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20India%20allegedly%20abstaining%20from%20all%20United%20Nations%20resolutions%20on%20Gaza%2C%20said%20that%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20on%20October%207%20last%20year%2C%2013%20resolutions%20concerning%20Palestine%20have%20been%20presented%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20(UNGA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20Israel-%20Hamas%20conflict%2C%2013%20resolutions%20concerning%20Palestine%20were%20brought%20in%20UNGA%20out%20of%20which%20India%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%2010%20resolutions%20and%20abstained%20from%20three%20resolutions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20provided%20significant%20humanitarian%20assistance%20to%20Palestine%20during%20the%20ongoing%20crisis.%20Since%20the%20conflict%20began%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20delivered%20approximately%2070%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20aid%2C%20including%2016.5%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20medicines%20and%20medical%20supplies%20in%20two%20tranches.%20Additionally%2C%20%245%20million%20was%20disbursed%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Relief%20and%20Works%20Agency%20for%20Palestinian%20Refugees%20in%20the%20Near%20East%20(UNRWA)%20in%202024%2C%20matching%20a%20similar%20contribution%20made%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20policy%20towards%20Palestine%20has%20been%20long-standing%20and%20we%20have%20always%20supported%20a%20negotiated%20two-State%20solution%2C%20towards%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%20and%20viable%20State%20of%20Palestine%20within%20secure%20and%20recognised%20borders%2C%20living%20side%20by%20side%20in%20peace%20with%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20shipments%20in%20October%20and%20November%202024%20included%2065%20tonnes%20of%20medical%20supplies%20sent%20to%20UNRWA%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Ministry%20of%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20that%20India%20has%20undertaken%20extensive%20diplomatic%20engagements%20to%20promote%20peace%20in%20the%20region.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20have%20communicated%20with%20leaders%20across%20the%20region%20and%20beyond%2C%20including%20high-level%20discussions%20with%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20counterparts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2022%2C%20PM%20Modi%20met%20with%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20during%20the%20Summit%20of%20the%20Future%20in%20New%20York%2C%20reiterating%20calls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20and%20renewed%20diplomatic%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20advocated%20for%20its%20position%20in%20international%20forums%2C%20including%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20BRICS%2C%20the%20Non-Aligned%20Movement%20(NAM)%2C%20and%20the%20Voice%20of%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733391360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fg5egdb8g_s-jaishankar-_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-gaza-india-supports-2-state-solution-s-jaishankar-on-israel-p