20and%20for%20airline%20services%20that%20offer%20passenger%20travel%20and%20goods%20delivery.%20Mahindra%20filed%20a%20trademark%20for%206e%2C%20for%20its%20BE%206e%20electric%20SUV%20in%20a%20class%20that%20is%20meant%20for%20motor%20vehicles%20and%20related%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FGsu3AU_XBrw%3Fsi%3DVwiC6vRLGN-iM5Qy%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Findigo-sues-mahindra-for-trademark-infringement-over-6e-branding-automaker-responds-7162893%5C%22%3EIndigo%20Files%20A%20Lawsuit%20Against%20Mahindra%20Over%20'6e'%20Trademark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20apparent%20that%20'6E'%20which%20is%20used%20by%20IndiGo%2C%20is%20a%20clever%20wordplay%20on%20'sexy'%20and%20Mahindra%20uses%20the%20same%20name%20with%20'BE'%2C%20which%20is%20short%20for%20Born%20Electric.%20So%2C%20the%20name%20of%20the%20electric%20SUV%20sounds%20similar%20to%20Mahindra%20'Be%20Sexy'.%20Now%20IndiGo%20believes%20that%20there%20is%20cause%20for%20confusion%20on%20part%20of%20its%20customers%20and%20Mahindra%20says%20that%20the%20name%20of%20its%20electric%20SUV%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20aviation%20and%20IndiGo%20and%20both%20trademarks%20operate%20in%20very%20different%20spaces%20and%20are%20very%20different%20entities.%20So%20there%20is%20no%20room%20or%20cause%20for%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOfficial%20statement%20addressing%20Indigo's%20trademark%20infringement%20claim%20over%20the%20usage%20of%20%26quot%3B6E%26quot%3B.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FXF9jq20GXW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FXF9jq20GXW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Mahindra%20Electric%20Origin%20SUVs%20(%40mahindraesuvs)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmahindraesuvs%2Fstatus%2F1863993517107753042%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20IndiGo%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20%26quot%3B6E%26quot%3B%20mark%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20IndiGo's%20identity%20for%20the%20past%2018%20years%20and%20is%20a%20registered%20trademark%20that%20holds%20strong%20global%20recognition.%20The%20%26quot%3B6E%26quot%3B%20mark%2C%20whether%20standalone%20or%20in%20its%20variants%20and%20formative%20forms%2C%20is%20extensively%20used%20by%20IndiGo%20for%20its%20offerings%20and%20for%20goods%20and%20services%20provided%20in%20collaboration%20with%20trusted%20partners.%26quot%3B%20They%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAny%20unauthorised%20use%20of%20the%20%26quot%3B6E%26quot%3B%20mark%2C%20whether%20standalone%20or%20in%20any%20form%2C%20constitutes%20an%20infringement%20of%20IndiGo's%20rights%2C%20reputation%2C%20and%20goodwill.%20IndiGo%20is%20committed%20to%20taking%20all%20necessary%20and%20appropriate%20steps%20to%20safeguard%20its%20intellectual%20property%20and%20brand%20identity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahindra%20%26amp%3B%20Mahindra%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BMahindra%20Electric%20Automobile%20Limited%2C%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20Company%20(%26quot%3BMEAL%26quot%3B)%2C%20revealed%20its%20electric%20origin%20SUVs%20the%20BE%206e%20and%20XEV%209e%20on%2026th%20November%2C%202024.%20MEAL%20has%20applied%20for%20trade%20mark%20registration%20under%20class%2012%20(vehicles)%20for%20%26quot%3BBE%206e%26quot%3B%20a%20part%20of%20its%20electric%20origin%20SUV%20portfolio.%26quot%3B%20They%20added.%20%26quot%3BHence%2C%20the%20Company%20does%20not%20see%20a%20conflict%20as%20Mahindra's%20mark%20is%20%26quot%3BBE%206e%2C%26quot%3B%20not%20the%20standalone%20%26quot%3B6E.%26quot%3B%20It%20differs%20fundamentally%20from%20Indigo's%20%26quot%3B6E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20represents%20an%20airline%2C%20eliminating%20any%20risk%20of%20confusion.%20The%20distinct%20styling%20further%20emphasizes%20their%20uniqueness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EM%26amp%3BM%20further%20clarified%20that%20they%20are%20in%20discussions%20with%20InterGlobe%20Aviation%20Limited%20to%20find%20an%20amicable%20solution.%20They%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Company%20has%20been%20transparently%20disclosing%20the%20material%20litigations%20on%20the%20company%20to%20the%20Stock%20Exchanges%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20compliance%20with%20the%20Listing%20Regulations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20the%20case%20titled%20Interglobe%20Aviation%20vs%20Mahindra%20Electric%20Automobile%20Limited%2C%20was%20presented%20before%20Justice%20Amit%20Bansal%20on%20Tuesday.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20is%20yet%20to%20pass%20a%20judgement%20on%20the%20case%20with%20the%20next%20hearing%20scheduled%20on%209%20December%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733391000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F5o843cj_indigo-mahindra_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Findigo-vs-mahindra-the-battle-of-6e-explained-7177795%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IndiGo%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Mahindra%20over%20the%20name%20of%20the%20BE%206e%20electric%20SUV%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20as%20the%20callsign%20of%20the%20low-cost%20airlines.%20Here's%20a%20lowdown%20on%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fauto%2Findigo-vs-mahindra-the-battle-of-6e-explained-7177795%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20senators%20call%20immigration%20system%20broken%2C%20proposes%20new%20cap%20%26amp%3B%20big%20changes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733