F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fdomain%2F3%2F2016%2F10%2F13062516%2FDevendra_Fadnavis_660-1.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20was%20mocked%20for%20being%20too%20self-assured%20and%20over-confident%20about%20being%20voted%20back%20to%20office%20with%20his%20%3Cem%3Emi%20punha%20yein%3C%2Fem%3E%20(I%20will%20return)%20campaign%20line.%20It%20had%20perhaps%20even%20ruffled%20his%20one-time%20ally%E2%80%94the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20then%20undivided%E2%80%94so%20much%20so%20that%20the%20two%20parted%20ways.%20Five%20years%20later%2C%20after%20leading%20his%20party%20to%20a%20historic%20victory%2C%20it%20was%20obvious%20that%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20would%20be%20the%20natural%20choice%20to%20become%20the%20chief%20minister%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIdeally%2C%20it%20should%20not%20have%20taken%20so%20much%20time%20to%20declare%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20he%20was%20always%20the%20BJP's%20first%20choice.%20However%2C%20the%20compulsions%20of%20coalition%20politics%20had%20forced%20the%20party%20to%20proceed%20cautiously%2C%20even%20as%20a%20saffron%20tsunami%20swept%20through%20the%20state.%20Sources%20within%20Maharashtra%20BJP%2C%20familiar%20with%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20agree%20that%20there%20was%20no%20alternative%20before%20the%20party%20leadership.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20victory%20could%20not%20have%20been%20achieved%20without%20him%20at%20the%20helm.%20This%20is%20why%2C%20while%20accepting%20the%20encomiums%20showered%20on%20him%2C%20Fadnavis%20tactfully%20affirmed%20the%20slogans%20%26quot%3BEk%20Hai%20To%20Safe%20Hai%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BModi%20Hai%20To%20Mumkin%20Hai%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECredit%20Where%20Due%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20an%20unmistakable%20stamp%20of%20Hindutva%20in%20his%20first%20speech%20after%20being%20entrusted%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20leading%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20government%20once%20again.%20His%20brief%20remarks%20acknowledged%20the%20kind%20of%20mandate%20the%20BJP%20had%20received%E2%80%94emerging%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%2C%20winning%20a%20record%20132%20out%20of%20288%20assembly%20seats.%20His%20comments%20recognised%20the%20efforts%20of%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20cadres%2C%20who%20worked%20silently%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20toiling%20from%20dawn%20to%20dusk%20to%20make%20this%20victory%20possible.%20RSS%20sources%20noted%20that%20it%20wasn't%20the%20first%20time%20Fadnavis%20had%20acknowledged%20the%20Sangh's%20role%20in%20the%20unprecedented%20poll%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20did%20refer%20to%20RSS's%20contribution%20right%20at%20the%20outset%20when%20he%20declared%20the%20role%20of%20various%20organisations%20that%20had%20contributed%20to%20the%20BJP's%20victory.%20Of%20course%2C%20he%20did%20not%20mention%20RSS%20by%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20pointed%20out%20an%20RSS%20functionary.%20Fadnavis%20struck%20a%20fine%20balance%20and%20noted%20that%20the%20Constitution%20%E2%80%9Cis%20sacrosanct%20to%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20PM%20Modi%20is%20keen%20that%20the%20new%20government%20should%20get%20down%20to%20business%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%20given%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20verdict.%20That%20is%20why%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20chose%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20as%20one%20of%20the%20central%20observers%20for%20the%20BJP%20legislators'%20meeting%20to%20elect%20a%20new%20chief%20minister.%20Sitharaman's%20presence%20set%20the%20development%20agenda%20for%20the%20new%20government.%20Soon%20after%20declaring%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20popular%20choice%20of%20the%20MLAs%2C%20Sitharaman%20brought%20the%20economic%20agenda%20of%20governance%20to%20the%20forefront.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%2C%20she%20described%20the%20Maharashtra%20verdict%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmandate%20for%20Viksit%20Bharat%26quot%3B.%20She%20highlighted%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Wadhwan%20port%20in%20Palghar%20with%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2076%2C000%20crore%20and%20also%20spoke%20about%20making%20Mumbai%20the%20fintech%20capital.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20decision%20of%2014%20crore%20people%20of%20Maharashtra%20sends%20a%20message%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country.%20This%20is%20not%20just%20a%20regular%20Assembly%20election.%20After%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20results%20of%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20have%20made%20the%20people's%20decision%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%20The%20overwhelming%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20was%20a%20result%20of%20frustration%20with%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20the%20previous%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20government%2C%20she%20added.%20She%20recalled%20how%20bullet%20trains%20could%20have%20become%20a%20reality%20in%20India%20if%20there%20had%20been%20no%20uncertainty%20following%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Caste%20Question%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20nagging%20doubts%20persist%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20state%20elections%20have%20brought%20closure%20to%20the%20disquiet%20in%20social%20equations.%20Would%20the%20return%20of%20Fadnavis%E2%80%94a%20Brahmin%20from%20Vidarbha%E2%80%94%20as%20CM%20once%20again%20not%20encourage%20dominant%20caste%20groups%20like%20the%20Marathas%20to%20exploit%20caste%20fault%20lines%3F%20Both%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20functionaries%20cite%20the%20emphatic%20victory%20across%20the%20state%20as%20proof%20that%20caste%20fault%20lines%20have%20been%20rendered%20irrelevant.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20elections%20have%20made%20the%20caste%20matrix%20irrelevant.%20The%20only%20thing%20that%20will%20matter%20is%20development%20and%20creation%20of%20more%20jobs%20and%20opportunities%20for%20the%20people.%20Our%20government%20will%20have%20to%20focus%20on%20deliveries%2C%E2%80%9D%20points%20out%20a%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20leader.%20The%20BJP's%20record%20performance%20in%20the%20caste%20cauldrons%20of%20Vidarbha%2C%20Marathwada%2C%20and%20North%20Maharashtra%20should%20exorcise%20the%20ghosts%20of%20caste%20warlords%20from%20the%20state%2C%20feel%20RSS%20strategists.%20The%20caste%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20hasn't%20been%20an%20issue%2C%20they%20assert.%20It%20was%20so%20only%20until%201995.%20That%20ended%20when%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20alliance%20rode%20to%20power%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20confidence%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20supremo%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20that%20he%20appointed%20Manohar%20Joshi%20as%20the%20first%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20the%20Mahayuti.%20He%20was%20not%20bothered%20about%20caste%20or%20region.%20He%20had%20supreme%20confidence%20in%20himself%3B%20he%20believed%20the%20mandate%20was%20for%20him.%20After%20Joshi%20moved%20out%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20(because%20of%20SC%20observations)%20in%20January%201999%2C%20some%20people%20advised%20Balasaheb%20to%20go%20for%20a%20Maratha%20CM.%20That's%20how%20he%20opted%20for%20Narayan%20Rane%E2%80%94a%20Maratha%20from%20the%20Konkan%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20pointed%20out%20a%20BJP%20leader.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20stayed%20out%20of%20power%20for%20nearly%2015%20years.%20We%20managed%20to%20return%20with%20the%20Modi%20wave.%20Fadnavis%20became%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20Congress%20gained%20from%20the%20mistake%20we%20made%20in%201999.%20As%20for%20civic%20elections%2C%20we%20don't%20want%20to%20worry.%20We%20did%20well%20in%202017%20under%20Fadnavis.%20We%20hope%20to%20do%20well%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20a%20party%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20sources%20believe%20that%20after%20the%202024%20assembly%20polls%2C%20Maharashtra%20could%20witness%20significant%20political%20realignment.%20There%20is%20speculation%20that%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Thackeray)%20and%20the%20Maharashtra%20Navnirman%20Sena%20(MNS)%20could%20come%20together.%20As%20for%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20patriarch%20of%20Maharashtra%20politics%20lost%20out%20mainly%20because%20he%20approached%20voters%20without%20a%20positive%20vision.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20highly%20respected%20but%20was%20seen%20targeting%20individual%20candidates%2C%20something%20that%20was%20missing%20in%20his%20nephew%20Ajitdada's%20outreach.%20People%20were%20put%20off%20by%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20observed%20one%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Lakshmi%20Iyer%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20been%20covering%20politics%20for%20four%20decades%20in%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20Mumbai.%20She%20is%20on%20X%20%40%3C%2Fem%3Eliyer%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733390520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fw.ndtvimg.com%2Fdomain%2F3%2F2016%2F10%2F13062516%2FDevendra_Fadnavis_660-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-devendra-fadnavis-emerged-as-a-cm-favourite-again-7177834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sources%20within%20Maharashtra%20BJP%20agree%20that%20there%20was%20no%20alternative%20before%20the%20party%20leadership.%20It%20had%20to%20be%20Fadnavis%20as%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20victory%20could%20not%20have%20been%20achieved%20without%20him%20at%20the%20helm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-devendra-fadnavis-emerged-as-a-cm-favourite-again-7177834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20data'%3A%20Govt%20caught%20short%20in%20Parl%20when%20pressed%20for%20data%20on%20critical%20issues%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733390441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116005710%2Cimgsize-1608639.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-data-in-digital-india-centre-caught-short-in-parliament-when-pressed-for-data-on-critical-issues%2Farticleshow%2F116002056.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government%20has%20admitted%20to%20Parliament%20a%20lack%20of%20centralized%20data%20on%20several%20crucial%20issues.%20This%20includes%20data%20on%20losses%20from%20natural%20calamities%2C%20suicides%20of%20medical%20interns%2C%20discrimination%20against%20SC%2FST%20students%2C%20and%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Donald%20Trump's%20Nominee%20Pete%20Hegseth%20Run%20Pentagon%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump's%20controversial%20nomination%20of%20TV%20host%20Pete%20Hegseth%20to%20run%20the%20Defense%20Department%20was%20teetering%20Wednesday%20as%20Republican%20senators%20raised%20questions%20over%20his%20fitness%20for%20the%20powerful%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20a%20former%20Army%20National%20Guard%20officer%20and%20Fox%20News%20weekend%20presenter%2C%20is%20under%20intense%20pressure%20over%20a%20series%20of%20misconduct%20allegations%2C%20including%20accusations%20of%20alcohol%20abuse%20and%20a%20sexual%20assault%20claim%20from%202017%2C%20over%20which%20no%20charges%20were%20filed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegseth%20denies%20all%20wrongdoing%20but%20the%20controversy%20has%20left%20Trump's%20transition%20officials%20scrambling%20to%20avoid%20the%20embarrassment%20of%20a%20second%20Cabinet%20nomination%20collapsing%20amid%20dwindling%20support%20from%20Republicans%20in%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERunning%20the%20Pentagon%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20roles%20in%20public%20office.%20The%20Defense%20Department%20employs%20almost%20three%20million%20military%20and%20civilian%20staff%2C%20and%20defense%20spending%20--%20including%20veterans'%20care%20--%20topped%20%241%2