to%20%26quot%3Bevade%20imminent%20investigations...%20into%20alleged%20illegal%20acts%20involving%20himself%20and%20his%20family%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20the%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBorn%20in%20dictatorship%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Seoul%20in%201960%20months%20before%20a%20military%20coup%2C%20Yoon%20studied%20law%20and%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20star%20public%20prosecutor%20and%20anti-corruption%20crusader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20Park%20Geun-hye%2C%20South%20Korea's%20first%20female%20president%2C%20being%20convicted%20of%20abuse%20of%20power%2C%20imprisoned%20and%20impeached%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20country's%20top%20prosecutor%20in%202019%2C%20he%20also%20indicted%20a%20top%20aide%20of%20Park's%20successor%2C%20Moon%20Jae-in%2C%20in%20a%20fraud%20and%20bribery%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conservative%20People%20Power%20Party%20(PPP)%2C%20in%20opposition%20at%20the%20time%2C%20liked%20what%20they%20saw%20and%20convinced%20Yoon%20to%20become%20their%20presidential%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20duly%20won%20in%20March%202022%2C%20beating%20Lee%20Jae-myung%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20but%20by%20the%20narrowest%20margin%20in%20South%20Korean%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHalloween%20to%20handbag%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20was%20never%20much%20loved%20by%20the%20public%2C%20in%20particular%20by%20women%20--%20he%20vowed%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20to%20abolish%20the%20ministry%20of%20gender%20and%20equality%20--%20and%20he%20has%20lurched%20from%20scandal%20to%20scandal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20included%20his%20administration's%20handling%20of%20a%202022%20crowd%20crush%20during%20Halloween%20festivities%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20150%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoters%20have%20also%20blamed%20Yoon's%20administration%20for%20food%20inflation%2C%20a%20lagging%20economy%20and%20increasing%20constraints%20on%20freedom%20of%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20accused%20of%20abusing%20presidential%20vetoes%2C%20notably%20to%20strike%20down%20a%20bill%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20a%20special%20investigation%20into%20alleged%20stock%20manipulation%20by%20his%20wife%20Kim%20Keon%20Hee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20suffered%20further%20reputational%20damage%20last%20year%20when%20his%20wife%20was%20secretly%20filmed%20accepting%20a%20designer%20handbag%20worth%20%242%2C000%20as%20a%20gift.%20Yoon%20insisted%20it%20would%20have%20been%20rude%20to%20refuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20mother-in-law%2C%20Choi%20Eun-soon%2C%20was%20sentenced%20to%20one%20year%20in%20prison%20for%20forging%20financial%20documents%20in%20a%20real%20estate%20deal.%20She%20was%20released%20in%20May%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20himself%20was%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20petition%20calling%20for%20his%20impeachment%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20which%20proved%20so%20popular%20the%20parliamentary%20website%20hosting%20it%20experienced%20delays%20and%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20sing!%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20have%20reported%20that%20Yoon%20is%20particularly%20enamoured%20of%20British%20wartime%20prime%20minister%20Winston%20Churchill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20president%2C%20Yoon%20has%20maintained%20a%20tough%20stance%20against%20nuclear-armed%20North%20Korea%20and%20bolstered%20ties%20with%20Seoul's%20traditional%20ally%2C%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20he%20sang%20Don%20McLean's%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20Pie%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20White%20House%2C%20prompting%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20respond%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20damn%20idea%20you%20could%20sing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20efforts%20to%20restore%20ties%20with%20South%20Korea's%20former%20colonial%20ruler%2C%20Japan%2C%20did%20not%20sit%20well%20with%20many%20at%20home%2C%20as%20the%