%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fpushpa-2-twitter-review-check-out-how-kollywood-fans-reacted-to-allu-arjun-and-rashmika-mandannas-film%2Farticleshow%2F115999794.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sea%20Of%20Toxic%20Foam%20In%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Hosur%20After%20Dam%20Discharges%20Surplus%20Water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20stretch%20of%20the%20South%20Pennai%20River%20near%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Hosur%20has%20transformed%20into%20a%20sprawling%20sea%20of%20toxic%20foam%20following%20the%20release%20of%20surplus%20water%20from%20the%20Kellavarapalli%20Dam.%20The%20discharge%2C%20prompted%20by%20heavy%20inflows%20from%20Karnataka%20after%20recent%20rains%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20severe%20environmental%20and%20public%20health%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20reveal%20alarming%20visuals%3A%20massive%20frothy%20waves%20coursing%20over%20the%20river's%20surface%2C%20foam%20swirling%20and%20spreading%20across%20nearby%20areas%2C%20and%20flurries%20of%20froth%20carried%20by%20the%20wind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20suspect%20the%20source%20lies%20in%20untreated%20industrial%20effluents%20from%20factories%20in%20neighbouring%20Karnataka%20straddling%20the%20Karnataka-Tamil%20Nadu%20border.%20These%20factories%20are%20believed%20to%20have%20exploited%20the%20heavy%20rains%20to%20dump%20pollutants%20into%20the%20water%20system%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20toxic%20buildup.%20The%20toxic%20foam%20poses%20significant%20threats%20to%20the%20river's%20ecosystem%2C%20aquatic%20life%2C%20and%20human%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20frothing%20event%20on%20the%20South%20Periyar%20River%20is%20part%20of%20a%20troubling%20pattern%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Professor%20Sacchida%20Nand%20Tripathi%2C%20Dean%20of%20the%20Kotak%20School%20of%20Sustainability.%20Prof%20Tripathi%20linked%20the%20event%20to%20%26quot%3Bexcessive%20organic%20loads%26quot%3B%20entering%20the%20river%20system%20due%20to%20untreated%20sewage%20and%20industrial%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20foam%20reduces%20dissolved%20oxygen%20levels%20in%20the%20water%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20death%20of%20fish%20and%20the%20destruction%20of%20algae%2C%20which%20are%20critical%20to%20the%20river's%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Prof%20Tripathi%20added.%20The%20foam%20also%20presents%20risks%20of%20waterborne%20diseases%20for%20nearby%20communities%20that%20rely%20on%20groundwater%20linked%20to%20the%20river%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20toxic%20foam%20has%20plagued%20Hosur.%20In%20October%2C%20heavy%20rain%20and%20reservoir%20discharges%20led%20to%20a%20similar%20incident%2C%20with%20five-foot-high%20froth%20spilling%20onto%20roads%2C%20disrupting%20traffic%2C%20and%20sparking%20cleanup%20efforts%20by%20emergency%20teams.%20Then%2C%20as%20now%2C%20authorities%20suspected%20industrial%20units%20in%20Karnataka%20were%20dumping%20effluents%20into%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kellavarapalli%20Dam%20incident%20mirrors%20similar%20frothing%20crises%20seen%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20including%20Bengaluru's%20Bellandur%20and%20Varthur%20Lakes%20and%20Delhi's%20Yamuna%20River.%20These%20events%20share%20common%20threads%3A%20untreated%20sewage%2C%20rampant%20industrial%20discharge%2C%20and%20weak%20regulatory%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733384580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fo146c12g_hosur-toxic-foam-_625x300_05_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsea-of-toxic-foam-in-tamil-nadus-hosur-after-dam-discharges-surplus-water-7177052%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20stretch%20of%20the%20South%20Periyar%20River%20near%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Hosur%20has%20transformed%20into%20a%20sprawling%20sea%20of%20toxic%20foam%20following%20the%20release%20of%20surplus%20water%20from%20the%20Kellavarapalli%20Dam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagemen