static.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115998893%2Cimgsize-97770.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpushpa-2-movie-review-and-release-live-updates-pushpa-2-allu-arjun-rashmika-mandanna-fahadh-faasil-priyamani-pushpa-2-the-rule-review%2Fliveblog%2F115998893.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115998893.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Six%20Hours%20of%20Turmoil%20That%20Shook%20South%20Korea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnc490tig_so_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%203%20at%2010%3A25%20pm%20Korean%20Standard%20Time%20(KST)%2C%20surprising%20news%20shocked%20the%20world%20as%20reports%20spread%20across%20social%20media%20announcing%20the%20imposition%20of%20Martial%20Law%20by%20the%20President%20of%20South%20Korea%2C%20Yoon%20Suk%20Yeol.%20The%20announcement%20was%20a%20shock%20for%20most%20South%20Koreans%2C%20who%20had%20long%20enjoyed%20the%20benefits%20of%20democracy%20and%20had%20only%20studied%20the%20imposition%20of%20martial%20law%20in%20history%20lessons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20prompted%20lawmakers%20and%20citizens%20to%20gather%20at%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20where%20the%20opposition%2C%20led%20by%20Lee%20Jae-myung%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20entered%20the%20assembly%20to%20vote%20on%20the%20president's%20decision.%20Armed%20troops%20attempted%20to%20enter%20the%20building%2C%20jostling%20with%20lawmakers%20and%20staff%2C%20but%20were%20unsuccessful%20in%20halting%20proceedings%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20vote%20rejecting%20the%20martial%20law.%20Following%20the%20National%20Assembly's%20decision%2C%20the%20President%20was%20forced%20to%20lift%20martial%20law%20at%204%3A40%20am%20KST%20on%20December%204%2C%20after%20an%20ordeal%20lasting%20six%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20declaration%20of%20emergency%20martial%20law%20was%20a%20surprise%2C%20it%20was%20not%20entirely%20unexpected.%20Many%20experts%20had%20already%20discussed%20the%20possibility%20of%20martial%20law%20being%20implemented%2C%20particularly%20after%20the%20recent%20appointment%20of%20close%20allies%20to%20Yoon's%20cabinet.%20This%20raised%20suspicions%20about%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98palace%20coup'.%20But%20what%20led%20to%20this%20extreme%20measure%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EReaction%20To%20Intensifying%20Pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Yoon's%20administration%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20misgovernance%20since%202022.%20For%20example%2C%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20doctors'%20protest%20and%20the%20Itaewon%20crowd%20disaster%20has%20faced%20widespread%20condemnation%20from%20both%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20public.%20In%20addition%20to%20governance%20issues%2C%20the%20First%20Lady%20has%20become%20a%20focal%20point%2C%20having%20been%20accused%20of%20corruption%2C%20scandals%2C%20and%20exerting%20undue%20influence%20within%20the%20presidential%20office.%20However%2C%20the%20situation%20grew%20more%20serious%20after%20the%20April%20National%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20when%20the%20opposition%20secured%20a%20majority%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20president's%20party%20to%20pass%20legislation%20and%20conduct%20normal%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20likely%20reason%20behind%20Yoon's%20extreme%20step%20was%20the%20growing%20pressure%20from%20all%20sides%2C%20including%20the%20Democratic%20Party%20(DP)%2C%20the%20public%2C%20and%20his%20own%20party.%20This%20pressure%20intensified%20in%20September%20when%20the%2022nd%20Assembly's%20first%20regular%20session%20began.%20Following%20that%2C%20Yoon%20faced%20increasing%20partisan%20strife%20as%20the%20assembly%20turned%20hostile%2C%20repeatedly%20demanding%20accountability%20from%20the%20president%20over%20actions%20taken%20against%20the%20First%20Lady.%20Just%20last%20week%2C%20the%20president%20vetoed%20a%20bill%20passed%20by%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20special%20counsel%20investigation%20into%20corruption%20charges%20against%20the%20First%20Lady.%20The%20tension%20between%20the%20president%20and%20the%20legislature%20also%20coincided%20with%20his%20declining%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20public%20address%20declaring%20martial%20law%2C%20he%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20declare%20martial%20law%20to%20protect%20the%20Republic%20of%20Korea%20from%20the%20threats%20of%20North%20Korean%20communist%20forces%2C%20to%20immediately%20eradicate%20the%20unscrupulous%20pro-Pyongyang%20antistate%20forces%20that%20pillage%20the%20freedom%20and%20happiness%20of%20our%20people%2C%20and%20to%20protect%20free%20constitutional%20order.%E2%80%9D%20He%20described%20the%20opposition's%20decision%20to%20block%20the%20National%20Assembly%20from%20functioning%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Clegislature%20dictatorship%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20had%20paralysed%20the%20administration%20and%20sabotaged%20state%20functions.%20The%20speech%20highlighted%20his%20frustration%20with%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20rising%20allegations%20against%20his%20wife%20and%20his%20falling%20popularity%2C%20the%20president%20also%20faced%20increasing%20pressure%20from%20within%20his%20party%2C%20particularly%20from%20Han%20Dong-hoon%2C%20the%20People%20Power%20Party%20(PPP)%20leader%20who%20publicly%20urged%20the%20president%20to%20take%20action.%20Sensing%20that%20he%20was%20losing%20support%20from%20the%20public%20and%20the%20party%2C%20and%20that%20the%20opposition's%20tactics%20were%20succeeding%2C%20he%20may%20have%20felt%20compelled%20to%20take%20this%20drastic%20step%2C%20which%20was%20supported%20only%20by%20a%20select%20few%20in%20the%20cabinet.%20As%20reported%20by%20the%20media%2C%20the%20Chungam%20Faction%E2%80%94a%20small%20group%20of%20close%20aides%2C%20including%20the%20president%20and%20the%20Defence%20Minister%E2%80%94took%20the%20decision%20without%20consulting%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20or%20the%20party.%20This%20indicates%20that%20the%20president%20felt%20he%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20declare%20martial%20law%20to%20save%20his%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Lies%20Ahead%20for%20Yoon%20and%20His%20Party%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20martial%20law%20was%20lifted%2C%20the%20entire%20cabinet%20offered%20to%20resign%20en%20masse.%20Several%20senior%20officials%20in%20the%20presidential%20offices%2C%20including%20the%20Presidential%20Chief%20of%20Staff%2C%20National%20Security%20Adviser%2C%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20for%20Policy%2C%20and%20seven%20others%2C%20have%20already%20submitted%20their%20resignations.%20The%20ruling%20party%2C%20PPP%2C%20has%20apologised%20for%20the%20president's%20decision%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20we%20deeply%20apologise%20to%20the%20public%20for%20this%20distressing%20situation%E2%80%9D%2C%20while%20its%20leader%2C%20Han%20Dong-hoon%2C%20has%20called%20for%20immediate%20action%20against%20Defence%20Minister%20Kim%20Yong-hyun%2C%20who%20was%20instrumental%20in%20making%20the%20decision%20alongside%20the%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20DP%2C%20the%20opposition%2C%20has%20not%20relented.%20It%20has%20doubled%20down%20after%20this%20incident%20and%20resolved%20to%20initiate%20impeachment%20proceedings%20against%20President%20Yoon%20if%20he%20refuses%20to%20resign%20immediately%2C%20calling%20his%20decision%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclear%20violation%20of%20the%20constitution%E2%80%9D%20and%20further%20stating%20that%20it%20constitutes%20%E2%80%9Ca%20serious%20act%20of%20rebellion%20and%20a%20perfect%20reason%20for%20impeachment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20impeachment%20process%20may%20take%20some%20time%2C%20beginning%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%20and%20then%20moving%20through%20the%20Constitutional%20Court%2C%20the%20first%20leg%20of%20the%20process%20is%20expected%20to%20proceed%20swiftly.%20Six%20parties%2C%20led%20by%20the%20opposition%20DP%2C%20have%20already%20submitted%20the%20impeachment%20bill%20yesterday%2C%20which%20will%20be%20listed%20today.%20The%20impeachment%20procedure%20requires%20a%20majority%20to%20propose%20a%20motion%20and%20support%20from%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20for%20it%20to%20pass.%20Although%20the%20DP%20holds%20170%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20it%20still%20requires%20200%20votes%20to%20secure%20the%20motion.%20Even%20with%20the%20support%20of%20smaller%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20New%20Reform%20Party%2C%20the%20number%20reaches%20only%20192%E2%80%94eight%20short%20of%20the%20expected%20total.%20Even%20if%20the%20motion%20passes%20through%20the%20National%20Assembly%2C%20the%20judicial%20process%20is%20likely%20to%20take%20much%20longer%20due%20to%20the%20procedural%20requirements%20for%20the%20Constitutional%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20opposition%20is%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20a%20serious%20investigation%20into%20the%20procedures%20surrounding%20the%20declaration%20of%20martial%20law%2C%20including%20examining%20the%20process%20behind%20the%20summoning%20of%20state%20council%20meetings%20for%20approval%2C%20with%20a%20view%20to%20supporting%20insurrection%20charges%20against%20the%20president.%20Nonetheless%2C%20what%20is%20certain%20is%20that%20the%20president's%20political%20career%20is%20likely%20over%20as%20a%20result%20of%20this%20decision.%20It%20will%20also%20have%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20prospects%20of%20his%20party%2C%20which%20was%20already%20plagued%20by%20serious%20allegations%20and%20internal%20conflict%20before%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20PPP%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20will%20oppose%20the%20president's%20impeachment%2C%20which%2C%20if%20it%20does%2C%20will%20further%20damage%20the%20party's%20reputation.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20adopting%20a%20%E2%80%98keep-at-arm's-length'%20approach%20by%20distancing%20itself%20from%20the%20president%20may%20help%20it%20save%20face.%20From%20this%20incident%2C%20which%20lasted%20only%20six%20hours%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20this%20political%20drama%20has%20showcased%20South%20Korea's%20remarkable%20democratic%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Abhishek%20Sharma%20is%20a%20Research%20Assistant%20with%20ORF%20and%20a%20PhD%20Candidate%C2%A0in%20Korean%20Studies%20at%20Delhi%20University.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733383920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnc490tig_so_625x300_04_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-story-of-south-koreas-six-hours-of-turmoil-7177068%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20the%20chaos%20that%20lasted%20only%20six%20hours%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20clear%3A%20this%20political%20drama%20has%20showcased%20South%20Koreas%20remarkable%20democratic%20resilience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fthe-story-of-south-koreas-six-hours-of-turmoil-7177068%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBest%20For%20Team...%26quot%3B%3A%20Rohit%20Makes%20Big%20Sacrifice%20Ahead%20Of%202nd%20Test%20vs%20Au