2engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fman-arrested-for-illegally-entering-salman-khans-film-set-threatens-to-call-lawrence-bishnoi%2Farticleshow%2F115998016.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Akalis'%20%26quot%3BState-Sponsored%26quot%3B%20Charge%20After%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20Fired%20At%2C%20AAP's%20Reply%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20Akali%20Dal%20chief%20Sukhbir%20Badal%20during%20his%20penance%20at%20Golden%20Temple%20yesterday%20has%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%2C%20with%20the%20Opposition%20party%20alleging%20a%20%26quot%3Bstate-sponsored%20attack%26quot%3B%20aimed%20at%20eliminating%20the%20%26quot%3Bmoderate%20leadership%26quot%3B%20of%20Sikhs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20serving%20penance%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20Akal%20Takht%20for%20mistakes%20committed%20during%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20regime%20in%20Punjab%20from%202007%20to%202017.%20He%20was%20performing%20sewadar%20duties%20at%20the%20entrance%20of%20Golden%20Temple%20yesterday%20when%20a%20man%20approached%20him%20and%20whipped%20out%20a%20firearm.%20The%20cops%20and%20devotees%20overpowered%20him.%20A%20bullet%20was%20fired%20but%20it%20hit%20the%20wall.%20The%20attacker%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Narain%20Singh%20Chaura%2C%20who%20has%20links%20with%20Khalistani%20terror%20outfit%20Babbar%20Khalsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20Opposition's%20criticism%20of%20Punjab's%20law%20and%20order%20situation%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20condemned%20the%20attack%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20the%20police's%20alertness%20that%20foiled%20it.%20Amritsar%20police%20commissioner%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Bhullar%20praised%20the%20cops%20for%20their%20swift%20response%20and%20underlined%20the%20challenges%20in%20deploying%20security%20personnel%20at%20the%20temple.%20He%20made%20another%20remark%20which%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20The%20top%20cop%20said%20they%20are%20also%20probing%20if%20the%20attack%20was%20orchestrated%20to%20generate%20a%20sympathy%20wave%20for%20the%20Akali%20Dal%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkalis%20Step%20Up%20Attack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Akali%20Dal%20leader%20Bikram%20Singh%20Majithia%20has%20released%20a%20video%20and%20said%20senior%20police%20officer%20Harpal%20Singh%20was%20seen%20shaking%20hands%20with%20the%20shooter%20the%20day%20before%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20an%20SP%20of%20Punjab%20Police%20shaking%20hands%20with%20someone%20who%20has%20a%20(criminal)%20history%3F%20if%20they%20had%20175%20police%20personnel%20there%2C%20why%20wasn't%20this%20guy%20caught%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%20Mr%20Majithia%20also%20slammed%20the%20Amritsar%20police%20commissioner%20for%20his%20'sympathy%20wave'%20remark.%20%26quot%3BMr%20Bhullar%2C%20the%20uniform%20will%20not%20stay%20forever%2C%20but%20will%20you%20be%20able%20to%20face%20people%20and%20look%20them%20in%20the%20eye%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20minister%20Daljit%20Singh%20Cheema%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20state-sponsored%20attack.%20There%20is%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20eliminate%20the%20moderate%20leadership%20of%20Sikhs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20direct%20attack%20on%20Chief%20Minister%20Mann%2C%20Mr%20Majithia%20drew%20parallels%20with%20the%202022%20murder%20of%20singer%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20after%20his%20security%20cover%20was%20withdrawn.%20%26quot%3BYou%20got%20Sidhu%20Moose%20Wala%20murdered%20by%20withdrawing%20his%20security.%20Anyone%20who%20opposes%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20his%20list%20of%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20have%20slammed%20the%20attack%20on%20Mr%20Badal%20and%20pointed%20to%20the%20deterioration%20of%20Punjab's%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%20State%20Congress%20chief%20Amarinder%20Singh%20Raja%20Warring%2C%20however%2C%20disagreed%20with%20the%20Akalis%20charge%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20eliminate%20its%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20tell%20you%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20finish%20Akali%20Dal%20leadership%20but%20I%20think%20there%20is%20nothing%20personal%20like%20that.%20A%20man%2C%20the%20individual%20who%20did%20that%20-%20who%20is%20he%2C%20who%20is%20he%20associated%20with%2C%20what%20institution%20he%20is%20affiliated%20to...%20what%20he%20had%20in%20mind%20and%20with%20what%20hatred%20he%20did%20that...%20We%20have%20condemned%20it%20that%20this%20should%20not%20happen...%20Where%20did%20this%20idea%20of%20eliminating%20Akali%20leaders%20come%20from%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mann%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BAlertness%20of%20cops%20foiled%20the%20attack.%20We%20have%20asked%20the%20police%20to%20conduct%20an%20in-depth%20investigation%20and%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20regular%20updates.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20supremo%20backed%20the%20party's%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20praised%20state%20police%20for%20averting%20a%20tragedy.%20%26quot%3BA%20very%20big%20tragedy%20was%20averted%20today%20because%20of%20the%20excellent%20work%20of%20the%20Punjab%20Police.%20I%20commend%20their%20alertness%2C%20which%20has%20set%20an%20example%20for%20the%20entire%20country%20on%20how%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20Delhi%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20said%20while%20the%20BJP%20talks%20about%20the%20Punjab%20incident%2C%20it%20remains%20silent%20on%20crime%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Punjab%2C%20we%20managed%20to%20prevent%20a%20tragedy.%20But%20in%20Delhi%2C%20murder%20cases%20are%20rising%2C%20shootouts%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20b