20them%20in%20activities%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20reading%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20use%20of%20Hindi%20and%20vernacular%20books%20to%20ensure%20cultural%20and%20linguistic%20relevance.%20These%20books%20are%20chosen%20to%20create%20a%20welcoming%20and%20fun%20learning%20environment%2C%20which%20encourages%20children%20to%20actively%20engage%20in%20the%20reading%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20is%20especially%20important%20as%20many%20of%20these%20children%20come%20from%20troubled%20homes%20to%20schools%20where%20corporal%20punishment%20is%20still%20common.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20sad%2C%20but%20the%20kind%20of%20environment%20they%20come%20from%20and%20the%20kind%20of%20environment%20they%20come%20to%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20are%20not%20heard%20and%20their%20opinions%20don%E2%80%99t%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20learning%20a%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20points%20out.%20By%20creating%20a%20space%20where%20children%20are%20encouraged%20to%20explore%2C%20engage%2C%20and%20voice%20their%20opinions%2C%20SABIA%20inculcates%20a%20love%20for%20reading%20and%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20world%20of%20stories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20always%20a%20rewarding%20experience%20to%20see%20the%20students%20actually%20be%20interested%20in%20books%20and%20learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman%20Mishra%2C%20supervisor%20of%20Holy%20Star%20School%20in%20Malad%2C%20Mumbai.%20%E2%80%9COur%20school%20is%20located%20in%20a%20community%20space%2C%20which%20has%20always%20been%20a%20challenge%20in%20terms%20of%20space%2C%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20dedicated%20library%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Suman%20is%20proud%20that%20the%20school%20has%20been%20able%20to%20accommodate%20a%20library%20for%20its%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20SABIA%20came%2C%20they%20turned%20our%20storeroom%2C%20where%20we%20kept%20supplies%2C%20into%20a%20small%20library%20by%20clearing%20half%20of%20the%20space%20and%20filling%20it%20with%20books%20our%20children%20could%20make%20use%20of.%E2%80%9D%20Since%20March%202024%2C%20about%20four%20volunteers%20have%20been%20visiting%20every%20Saturday%2C%20each%20working%20with%2010%20to%2015%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20children%20proudly%20holding%20up%20their%20drawings%2C%20created%20with%20the%20help%20of%20SABIA%20volunteers%2C%20showcasing%20their%20creativity%20and%20talent.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTrivenisessions_jaipur_11zon-1732781398-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383824%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECreating%20a%20dynamic%20and%20encouraging%20environment%20to%20make%20learning%20a%20better%20experience%20for%20children%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESABIA%20believes%20in%20building%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20movement%20where%20individuals%20come%20with%20the%20heart%20and%20intention%20of%20helping%2C%20and%20volunteers%20form%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20operations.%20In%202024%20alone%2C%20they%20had%20a%20team%20of%20200%20volunteers%20who%20worked%20with%20and%20were%20able%20to%20enrich%20the%20reading%20experience%20for%20over%20500%20students%20in%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBackend%20to%20frontend%2C%20everything%20is%20done%20by%20volunteers.%20We%20have%20a%20core%20team%2C%20but%20only%20two%20of%20us%20are%20full-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20reached%20over%2030%2C000%20children%20across%20175%20schools%20in%2016%20states.%20The%20group%E2%80%99s%20community%20libraries%20in%20cities%20like%20Kota%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20and%20Delhi%2C%20housing%20more%20than%205%2C000%20books%2C%20recently%20welcomed%20232%20new%20members.%20SABIA%20also%20improved%20library%20spaces%20in%20schools%20across%20Delhi%20and%20Noida%2C%20and%20established%20its%20first%20model%20school%20library%20in%20Jaipur%20that%20houses%20books%20and%20serves%20as%20a%20space%20where%20children%20can%20learn%2C%20creatively%20engage%20themselves%20or%20study.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20organisation%20hosted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311547%2Fdelhi-jasmine-anoop-start-storytelling-initiative-for-children-in-rural-himachal-pradesh-villages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estorytelling%20sessions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20public%20and%20low-budget%20private%20schools%20in%20and%20around%20Jaipur%2C%20conducted%20by%20a%20team%20of%2014%20storytellers.%20These%20sessions%20focused%20on%20perspective%2C%20empathy%2C%20and%20creative%20thinking%2C%20helping%20the%20children%20develop%20important%20life%20skills%20and%20a%20love%20for%20literature.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChallenges%2C%20and%20the%20road%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20challenges%20remain.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20highlighted%20the%20digital%20divide%20that%20exists%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20several%20children%20lacking%20access%20to%20the%20internet%20or%20technology%20for%20online%20learning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COut%20of%2025%2C000%20children%20we%20worked%20with%2C%20only%201%2C000%20could%20sign%20up%20for%20online%20sessions%2C%20and%20just%20300%20were%20regular%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20admits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20lockdown%20measures%20eased%2C%20SABIA%20managed%20to%20set%20up%20community%20spaces%20and%20adapt%20to%20the%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20set%20up%20a%20library%20space%20in%20my%20own%20home%2C%20and%20later%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20I%20opened%20a%20home%20library%20there%20too.%20This%20space%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20children%20engaged%20in%20learning%20even%20when%20their%20school%20had%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti%2C%20recounting%20the%20story%20of%20Anita%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20two%20girls%20who%2C%20despite%20being%20out%20of%20school%20for%20years%20due%20to%20COVID%2C%20were%20able%20to%20c