n%20arrived%2C%20he%20found%20not%20only%20the%20two%20deer%20trapped%20and%20dead%20but%20also%20the%20heartbreaking%20sight%20of%20another%20deer%20helplessly%20waiting%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20fence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deer%20has%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20coexisting%20with%20the%20farming%20community%20and%20the%20lands%2C%20and%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20it%20has%20been%20cast%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wildlife%20that%20once%20flourished%20around%20them%20is%20disappearing%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20local%20community%20to%20step%20up%20and%20protect%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20does%20not%20matter%20to%20me%20if%20a%20sanctuary%20has%205%2C000%20deer.%20I%20want%20this%20place%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20to%20be%20a%20healthy%20ecosystem%20like%20it%20was%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20filled%20with%20emotion.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20biodiversity%20needs%20its%20own%20plantation%20and%20wildlife%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that%20deserves%20to%20be%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sharvan%20Patel%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732717800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D383592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wildlife%20conservationist%20Sharvan%20Patel%20is%20using%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20of%201%2C000%20members%2C%20each%20contributing%20Rs%20365%20annually%2C%20to%20restore%20habitats%2C%20protect%20endangered%20species%2C%20and%20improve%20farming%20practices%20in%20Rajasthan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20Plastic%20Piles%20on%20the%20Delhi-Jaipur%20Highway%2C%202%20Friends%20Created%20Waste-Based%20Cement%22%2C%22content